{"tid":1070770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚肥絲大隻，想問到底點樣用粵語正字先啱？","createTime":"2019-03-21T02:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T09:21:30.000Z","uid":89887,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"23e430b49924fb2723a56a449c85a77226cc6a18","tid":1070770,"uid":89887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"其實一直都對打粵語嘅字有疑問<br />\n就係點樣先叫做正字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有人話咩文字係約定俗成<br />\n咁即係錯得多就okay，唔需要理正字啦？<br />\n咁嘅話又好似無分對錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似隨手上網搵篇文見到幅圖話十個錯字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob//Content/Upload/Charts/ReplaceImages/2019-03/a0d60b5d-e390-4643-824e-6ddf38765f7c_re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2F%2FContent%2FUpload%2FCharts%2FReplaceImages%2F2019-03%2Fa0d60b5d-e390-4643-824e-6ddf38765f7c_re.png&h=c81b9ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似「系」係古字有係嘅意思<br />\n而家大家都話係錯咁<br />\n愈諗愈唔明，愈諗愈頭痛<br />\n想請問吓各位有咩高見指點吓小弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f5ed0cd849cb19f38755b6495a653e63059c43","tid":1070770,"uid":89887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"btw,補返條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/03/18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdailyview.tw%2Fhk%2FDaily%2F2019%2F03%2F18&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=341d55ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/03/18</a>"},{"pid":"6526bee4d5f73db4ee1066169c3db4f70e545175","tid":1070770,"uid":238404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"每次見到個牙字都覺得好唔順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /